    "Although the training methodology is straightforward and simple, the extensive computational demands have restricted the creation of LLMs to a select few.",
    "That is why none of the open-source LLMs such as BLOOM, LLaMA-1 and Falcon could made a suitable substitutes for closed-source LLMs [39].",
    "More recently, responding to this demand, LLaMA-2 and LLaMA-3 were introduced, which are a family of pretrained and fine-tuned LLMs at scales up to 70B parameters [39].",
